name: .MFP File Extension
summary: Learn about .MFP files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: An MFP file is a custom disc or case label created with with MediaFACE label design software. MFP files are typically created from a template (.MFT) file and formatted for a specific label printing sheet. Each MFP file may include both images and text.
